    Fix matching engine: channel normalization + batch matching rewrite
    
    - iPOS and Bank POS now treated as the same channel for matching
      (sales use 'iPOS', receipts use 'Bank POS' — same money flow)
    - Tier 5 rewritten: greedily sums unmatched sales per receipt
      instead of matching daily totals (handles partial bank batches)
    - Channel normalization applied to Tiers 2, 3, 4, and 5
    - Skip noise rows during ingestion (Opening Balance, Closing, Totals)
    - Allow application/CDFV2 MIME type for old .xls files
    - Add CSRF token to delete upload fetch() calls
    
