    - 5-tier matching engine (exact, amount+date, fuzzy, split, batch)
    - Variance reporting with Ready/Attention/All triage tabs
    - Formal statement lifecycle with maker-checker approval
    - Escalation queue for managers
    - CSRF, rate limiting, 2FA, session hardening, password policy
    - Global search, CSV export, bulk actions
    - Dashboard with Chart.js trends
    - Role-based access (Uploader, Reconciler, Manager, Admin)
    
